title: Complete Hajj Method in Urdu/Hindi and Persian/Farsi
description:
Dear Friends,

 For all those who are going to offer hajj in Mecca and are looking for video(s) to learn the whole hajj method in detail, here it is, and the good thing is that it's in the local sub-continent languages i.e. Urdu/Hindi and Persian/Farsi/Dari.

 Please keep seeding it so that many more can get benefited from this torrent and do share your feedback.
